headline: Nasdaq Reports December 2024 Volumes and 4Q24 Statistics
summary: NEW YORK, Jan. 08, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Nasdaq (Nasdaq: NDAQ) today reported monthly volumes for December 2024, as well as quarterly volumes, estimated revenue capture, number of listings, and index statistics for the quarter ended December 31, 2024 on its Investor Relations website. A data sheet showing this information can be found at: http://ir.nasdaq.com/financials/volume-statistics.
